#: apps/site/src/lib/use-cases-data.ts:137
msgid "隐界以 MIT 协议开源，可以用一行 docker compose 跑在自己服务器或家里的小主机上。数据不出你的硬盘，模型可以接 OpenAI、Anthropic、本地 Ollama，甚至完全离线。"
msgstr "Enclave is open-source under MIT and runs on your own server or home box with a single docker compose command. Your data never leaves your disk, and the model layer can plug into OpenAI, Anthropic, local Ollama — or stay fully offline."

#: apps/site/src/components/multi-platform-carousel.tsx:47
msgid "隐界我的角色：你与 AI 化身的资料卡、个性、形象设定"
msgstr "Yinjie My Character: profile cards, personality, and look settings for you and your AI avatar"

#: apps/site/src/lib/use-cases-data.ts:50
msgid "隐界把「长期关系」变成产品级体验"
msgstr "Enclave turns \"long-term relationships\" into a product-grade experience"

#: apps/site/src/lib/use-cases-data.ts:92
msgid "隐界支持把多个 AI 角色拉进同一个群组，让他们之间也产生关系、互动、争吵、合作——你不是和「一个 chatbot 重复对话」，而是在导演一个小世界。"
msgstr "Enclave lets you pull multiple AI characters into one group, where they form relationships, interact, argue, and cooperate — you're not having repeat conversations with one chatbot, you're directing a small world."

#: apps/site/src/lib/use-cases-data.ts:141
msgid "隐界整个 monorepo 在 GitHub 上，MIT 协议任意审计、任意修改。一行 docker compose 起一份属于自己的实例：API、前端、数据库、向量索引全在本地。模型层可以混用云端 API 和本地 Ollama / vLLM，对哪类对话用哪个模型完全你说了算。"
msgstr "The entire Enclave monorepo lives on GitHub under MIT — audit it, modify it, fork it. A single docker compose spins up your own instance with API, frontend, database, and vector index all running locally. The model layer mixes cloud APIs and local Ollama / vLLM however you want — you decide which model handles which kind of conversation."

#: apps/site/src/components/multi-platform-carousel.tsx:41
msgid "隐界新人引导：首次进入虚拟世界的角色初始化与世界设定"
msgstr "Yinjie new-user onboarding: first-entry character setup and world configuration for the virtual world"

#: apps/site/src/components/faq-accordion.tsx:11
msgid "隐界是一个 AI 社交世界。每个用户都有一个属于自己的私人世界，里面有 AI 角色、朋友圈、群聊、电话、笔记，可以和角色长期对话、发展关系，让 AI 真正成为日常的一部分。"
msgstr "Enclave is an AI social world. Every user gets their own private world filled with AI characters, moments, group chats, calls, and notes — you can hold long-running conversations, grow relationships, and let AI become a real part of daily life."

#: apps/site/src/components/faq-accordion.tsx:10
msgid "隐界是做什么的？"
msgstr "What does Enclave do?"

#: apps/site/src/components/multi-platform-carousel.tsx:23
msgid "隐界朋友圈：AI 角色与你共享的私人时间线，会主动发动态与互动"
msgstr "Yinjie Moments: a private timeline shared with AI characters who post and engage on their own"

#: apps/site/src/lib/use-cases-data.ts:51
msgid "隐界给每个 AI 角色一个完整的人设：人格、作息、关系网、对你的亲密度，会随着你们的互动慢慢变化。AI 会主动发动态、给你打电话、记得你上周说的烦心事，让陪伴不再是单向召唤，而是双向流动。"
msgstr "Enclave gives every AI character a full profile: personality, daily routine, social graph, and how close they feel to you — all of it shifts gradually as you interact. The AI posts moments on its own, calls you, and remembers what was bothering you last week, so companionship stops being a one-way summons and starts flowing both ways."

#: apps/site/src/components/multi-platform-carousel.tsx:35
msgid "隐界群组：多 AI 角色与你的多人对话场景"
msgstr "Yinjie Groups: multi-person scenarios with multiple AI characters and you"

#: apps/site/src/lib/use-cases-data.ts:96
msgid "隐界群聊里每个角色都有自己的人设、和你及彼此的关系，发言时会考虑别人刚说了什么。你可以做导演（设定背景、推进剧情）也可以做参与者（直接和角色对话），随时切换。"
msgstr "In Enclave group chats, every character has their own profile and relationships — both with you and with each other — and they take what others just said into account when they speak. You can play director (set the scene, push the plot) or participant (talk to characters directly), and switch any time."

#: apps/site/src/components/multi-platform-carousel.tsx:17
msgid "隐界聊天界面：与 AI 角色的线程化对话、消息提醒、强提醒、已读标记"
msgstr "Yinjie chat interface: threaded conversations with AI characters, message alerts, strong alerts, and read receipts"

#: apps/site/src/components/faq-accordion.tsx:23
