msgstr "First cadence update after the public launch — upgrading from \"it runs\" to \"a stranger can open it and have a smooth time.\""

#: apps/site/src/lib/use-cases-data.ts:73
msgid "默认会一直记着；隐界用结构化记忆系统而不是简单上下文窗口，所以即使聊了几个月，关键事件依然能被引用。你也可以随时查看、编辑、删除任何记忆条目。"
msgstr "By default, forever. Enclave uses a structured memory system rather than a simple context window, so key events stay quotable even months in. You can view, edit, or delete any memory entry at any time."
